1
00:00:56,359 --> 00:00:57,039
Yunfei

2
00:00:58,759 --> 00:00:59,240
I'm here.

3
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,640
Don't tell my dad

4
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:03,840
what happened today.

5
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:10,400
Why does he always pick on you?

6
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,040
It's nothing.

7
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:14,840
My uncle is just like that.

8
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:18,560
Then I'll go to him again.

9
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:19,439
Don't go.

10
00:01:21,719 --> 00:01:22,719
I'll go.

11
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:26,239
What if he bullies you?

12
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,680
He doesn't bully you anyway.

13
00:01:32,519 --> 00:01:33,840
Why do you always push me away?

14
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:37,200
I told you not to get involved in this.

15
00:01:58,959 --> 00:02:00,359
You can't wear those clothes anymore.

16
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:02,920
I just had some clothes delivered to you.

17
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:04,760
They're your size.

18
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:04,800
Give me the money.

19
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:06,919
You have a life on your hands.

20
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:18,639
Xiaochuan.

21
00:05:30,759 --> 00:05:31,680
You didn't come home last night.

22
00:05:31,839 --> 00:05:32,959
Xiaochuan didn't suspect anything, did she?

23
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:35,000
She didn't ask about it.

24
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,160
Our daughter

25
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:37,240
is sensible.

26
00:05:37,279 --> 00:05:37,800
Go.

27
00:05:40,279 --> 00:05:42,519
Why didn't she come to work today?

28
00:05:42,839 --> 00:05:44,000
She's on a rest day.

29
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:52,439
He Gu acupoint is mainly for headache.

30
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,600
Xiaochuan, don't you have a rest day today?

31
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,279
I've had it.

32
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,000
What's wrong with her today?

33
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,480
Don't keep staring at her, it's annoying.

34
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:09,800
Fine.

35
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,560
Come, let me check your pulse.

36
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:16,319
Xiaofei, why are you here?

37
00:06:16,319 --> 00:06:16,800
Stomachache.

38
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:19,600
Stomachache?

39
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:46,639
What's wrong?

40
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:48,920
I caught a cold last night.

41
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:55,560
What's wrong with Xiaochuan?

42
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,680
Is he sick?

43
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,439
Summer is prone to colds.

44
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,079
Xiaochuan, I'll make you some herbal tea.

45
00:07:18,519 --> 00:07:18,959
It's okay.

46
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:20,439
No fever.

47
00:07:23,079 --> 00:07:23,639
What's wrong?

48
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:26,519
There's someone.

49
00:07:26,839 --> 00:07:27,519
So what?

50
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,920
So,

51
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:31,959
we should keep our distance.

52
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:38,600
If you don't know how to tell them,

53
00:07:39,399 --> 00:07:40,160
I'll do it.

54
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,600
As for us,

55
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,519
maybe we should

56
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,040
just forget it,

57
00:07:57,839 --> 00:07:58,439
okay?

58
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:04,199
My dad's getting married soon,

59
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,680
and it's not a good idea

60
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,160
for us to be together.

61
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:09,800
Besides,

62
00:08:11,079 --> 00:08:12,639
I haven't thought it through

63
00:08:12,839 --> 00:08:13,759
about what happened yesterday.

64
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,279
It was just

65
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,959
an accident.

66
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,240
Accident?

67
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,439
So, what's the reason

68
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,759
this time?

69
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,720
Here's your winter melon tea.

70
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:42,559
It clears heat and removes dampness.

71
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:43,840
Okay.

72
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:44,600
Drink it while it's hot.

73
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:46,440
Okay.

74
00:08:47,399 --> 00:08:48,639
I'm not scolding you.

75
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,080
You're a doctor yourself.

76
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,799
You should know better than to overwork yourself.

77
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:54,039
Was the air conditioning on all night last night?

78
00:08:54,519 --> 00:08:55,159
It's possible.

79
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:57,480
Last night,

80
00:08:59,200 --> 00:08:59,960
it was quite hot.

81
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,360
What's wrong?

82
00:09:02,759 --> 00:09:03,639
Dad, this...

83
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,279
It's too hot.

84
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:05,679
I'll go.

85
00:09:05,799 --> 00:09:06,840
I'll do it.

86
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:07,799
You take a rest.

87
00:09:08,039 --> 00:09:08,519
Dad.

88
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,799
Why are you nervous?

89
00:09:18,639 --> 00:09:19,559
Are you afraid I'll mention last night?

90
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:40,600
Give it back to me.

91
00:09:41,879 --> 00:09:42,799
It's for me.

92
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,080
Why do you give it to you?

93
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:47,440
Thank you, Doctor Lan.

94
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:57,360
Yunfei,

95
00:09:57,919 --> 00:09:58,679
did you hear clearly

96
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:00,000
what I just told you?

97
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:02,759
No.

98
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:03,919
Can you say it again?

99
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,559
I mean,

100
00:10:05,799 --> 00:10:06,840
between us,

101
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:07,840
it's...

102
00:10:07,879 --> 00:10:08,480
What do you want to do?

103
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,440
It's not up to you

104
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,440
to decide what we do.

105
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,120
Are you a zombie?

106
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:26,279
Take it.

107
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:41,919
This time,

108
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,159
I won't let you go.
